(2) Claims for contributions to an employee benefit plan entitled to priority under section 507(a)(5).

(a) Except as provided in section 510 of this title, property of the estate shall be distributed—(1) first, in payment of claims of the kind specified in, and in the order specified in, section 507 of this title, proof of which is timely filed under section 501 of this title or tardily filed on or before the earlier of—(A) the date that is 10 days after the mailing to creditors of the summary of the trustee’s final report; or

